                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-grey bg-grey-300">
                        <div class="entry-content__grid text-center white">
                            <h3>h3 title</h3>
                            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Doloribus eum necessitatibus nihil ratione tempora? Ab aliquam ea enim error expedita explicabo ipsam nam provident ut veniam. Eligendi esse itaque quibusdam?</p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn" title="button title" target="_blank">Button</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

